[32m+[m[32m## üîç Using the Scanner[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mWe provide a Go-based tool that scans your dependencies and matches them against the OSV database using the OSV API.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Capabilities[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Scans lockfiles[m
[32m+[m[32m- Scans Debian Docker containers[m
[32m+[m[32m- Scans SBOMs (SPDX / CycloneDX)[m
[32m+[m[32m- Scans Git repositories[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Scanner Repository[m
 [m
[31m-## Documentation[m
[32m+[m[32m- https://github.com/google/osv-scanner[m
 [m
[31m-Comprehensive documentation is available [here](https://google.github.io/osv.dev).[m
[31m-API documentation is available [here](https://google.github.io/osv.dev/api/).[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
